{
  "stem": "7781.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took those people to Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the clothes used to come back to the ghetto to be sorted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then they brought in the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought Jews from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you see, the population got less, you know, due to hunger and starvation, deportation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they made-- Lodz was like a holding pen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know-- they-- if they needed Jews to a certain amount to be exterminated, they didn't have to go to look for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would come to the ghetto and say to them, we need 10,000 Jews, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you provide for-- for resettlement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they didn't have to go, you know, look around for the 10,000 Jews, little villages here and there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were right there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So Lodz was like a holding pen for the machinery, for the-- for the destructive machinery that was going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They brought in Jews from-- from-- from Germany, from Czechoslovakia, from Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those Jews, when they came, they lived as free until they got to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they got to the ghetto, all of a sudden, when it hit them, the conditions, they hardly could take it because that was-- they-- they lived a normal-- you know, they had food.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they arrived, they had lived in Germany, they came to the ghetto, we lived already on a starvation diet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were more adjusted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we-- we slowly got into that way of life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they came in, and they didn't know what to-- where-- they came into ghetto, and they, all of a sudden, they were confronted with a different way of life.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that was a shock to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very hard on them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
